-- TAKE A LOOK-Protesters in Hong Kong demand full democracy 
-- 
-- Fri Oct 03, 2014 07:08AM EDT
-- None



Oct 3 (Reuters) - Tens of thousands of people have taken to Hong Kong's streets to demand full democracy in the former British colony, including a free voting system when they come to choose a new leader in 2017.

